    "body": "The forks after the merge are actually scheduled by slot on the cl, so we need to activate the same fork on the EL at the same slot. The slotnumber itself is based on a timestamp. \r\nSee also the EIP for it: https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-6122",
